ton button-xxx&quot;&gt;</strong>This  is link text.<strong>&lt;/a&gt;</strong>, where <strong>xxx</strong> is the button color name selected from: <strong>light</strong>, <strong>dark</strong>, <strong>green</strong>, <strong>yellow</strong>, <strong>blue</strong> and <strong>red</strong>.</p>\r\n <p><span class=\"text-highlight highlight-light\"><strong>Example:</strong></span> <strong>&lt;a  class=&quot;link-button button-yellow&quot;&gt;</strong>See plans &amp; pricing.<strong>&lt;/a&gt;</strong></p>\r\n <h4>Combination of Button and Icon Styles</h4>\r\n <p>You can use both button and icon link style combined.</p>\r\n <div class=\"grid-layout\">\r\n  <div>\r\n    <p><a href=\"#\" class=\"link-button button-light\"><span class=\"link-icon fa fa-home\"> Button &amp; Home icon</span></a></p>\r\n    <p><a href=\"#\" class=\"link-button button-dark\"><span class=\"link-icon fa fa-calendar\"> Button &amp; Calendar icon</span></a></p>\r\n    <p><a href=\"#\" class=\"link-button button-blue\"><span class=\"link-icon fa fa-email\"> Button &amp; Mail icon</span></a></p>\r\n  </div>\r\n  <div>\r\n    <p><a href=\"#\" class=\"link-button button-green\"><span class=\"link-icon fa fa-image\"> Button &amp; Image icon</span></a></p>\r\n    <p><a href=\"#\" class=\"link-button button-yellow\"><span class=\"link-icon fa fa-user\"> Button &amp User icon</span></a></p>\r\n    <p><a href=\"#\" class=\"link-button button-red\"><span class=\"link-icon fa fa-star\"> Button &amp; Star icon</span></a></p>\r\n  </div>\r\n  <div>\r\n    <p><a href=\"#\" class=\"link-button button-brrown\"><span class=\"link-icon fa fa-link\"> Button &amp Link icon</span></a></p>\r\n    <p><a href=\"#\" class=\"link-button button-purple\"><span class=\"link-icon fa fa-search\"> Button &amp; Search icon</span></a></p>\r\n  </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p><span class=\"text-highlight highlight-light\"><strong>Usage:</strong></span> <strong>&lt;a class=&quot;link-button button-xxx&quot;&gt;&lt;span  class=&quot;link-ic